description: Removes the specified list of account IDs from the given billing group.

parameters.name: Arn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the billing group that the array of account IDs will disassociate from.

parameters.name: AccountIds
parameters.description: The array of account IDs to disassociate. (string) ---

nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the billing group that the array of account IDs is disassociated from.
